Sales Analysis Dashboard (Excel Project)
Project Overview
This project is an interactive Excel dashboard designed to analyze coffee sales performance, customer purchasing behavior, and regional sales trends. The dashboard transforms raw transactional data into actionable business insights using Excel-based data analytics and visualization techniques.
The project demonstrates practical business intelligence and data analysis skills including:
•	Data cleaning and transformation
•	Data modeling using multiple datasets
•	KPI development
•	Sales trend analysis
•	Customer segmentation
•	Interactive dashboard creation in Excel
•	Business performance reporting
________________________________________
Objective
The primary objective of this project is to:
•	Analyze coffee sales performance across products and regions
•	Identify top-performing customers and products
•	Monitor sales trends over time
•	Evaluate customer purchasing patterns
•	Build an interactive dashboard for business decision-making
________________________________________
