Dataset Overview
The project uses multiple related datasets to build a structured sales reporting system.
________________________________________
1. Orders Dataset (orders)
Contains transactional sales data for coffee orders.
Data Structure
Column Name	Description	Data Type
Order ID	Unique order identifier	String
Order Date	Date of purchase	Date
Customer ID	Unique customer identifier	String
Product ID	Unique product identifier	String
Quantity	Quantity purchased	Integer
Customer Name	Customer full name	String
Email	Customer email address	String
Country	Customer country	String
Coffee Type	Coffee category code	String
Roast Type	Roast category code	String
Size	Product package size	Numeric/String
Unit Price	Price per unit	Decimal
Sales	Total sales amount	Decimal
Coffee Type Name	Coffee category description	String
Roast Type Name	Roast category description	String
Loyalty Card	Loyalty membership status	String
